<item>
            <title>[LU-183] error: get_param: /proc/{fs,sys}/{lnet,lustre}/osd/*MDT0000/kbytesfree: Found no match</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-183</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Lustre test scripts on master branch need to be fixed to use osd-ldiskfs instead of osd in the proc path.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;One failure instance is as follows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== sanity test 57b: default LOV EAs are stored inside large inodes =================================== 20:47:54 (1301543274)
mcreating 100 files
total: 100 creates in 0.19 seconds: 520.27 creates/second
Filesystem           1K-blocks      Used Available Use% Mounted on
client-16-ib@o2ib:/lustre
                      11811168    502128  10708644   5% /mnt/lustre
client-16-ib: error: get_param: /proc/{fs,sys}/{lnet,lustre}/osd/*MDT0000/kbytesfree: Found no match
opening files to create objects/EAs
Filesystem           1K-blocks      Used Available Use% Mounted on
client-16-ib@o2ib:/lustre
                      11811168    502128  10708644   5% /mnt/lustre
client-16-ib: error: get_param: /proc/{fs,sys}/{lnet,lustre}/osd/*MDT0000/kbytesfree: Found no match
Resetting fail_loc on all nodes...done.
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
